# `go build ./...` from the repo root drops a `protoregistry` binary
# here (the cmd/protoregistry package output). Leading `/` anchors the
# pattern to the repo root so cmd/protoregistry and proto/protoregistry
# (which are source dirs) aren't matched.
/protoregistry

